## Privacy policy for Aruco Remote

- The application only connects to the server specified by the user (via scanning a QR code).
- Only the coordinates of markers and touches are sent over the network. Captured images are processed on the device.
- [Source code](https://github.com/bndeff/aruco) of the application is available for independent review.
- Image processing is performed using the [OpenCV](https://github.com/opencv/opencv) library. Binaries included in the app are from the
  [official build bot](https://pullrequest.opencv.org/buildbot/export/opencv_releases/master-contrib_pack-contrib-android/), artifact id
  [11383](https://pullrequest.opencv.org/buildbot/export/opencv_releases/master-contrib_pack-contrib-android/20220327-052314--11383/OpenCV4Android.zip).
